  "description": "Torus T(3,2) encodes a perfect fifth (3:2 frequency ratio) into the FDN delay length ratios. Voices lock into a stable fifth-based harmonic lattice — resonances that reinforce rather than fight each other. Tangle at 0.5, entrain at 0.5: the fifth is present and alive. The most harmonically stable Torus config.",
